  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "ASh-12 12.7x55 突击步枪",
      "en": "ASh-12 12.7x55 assault rifle"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "ASh-12",
      "en": "ASh-12"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "ASh-12.7（即俄语“12.7 口径突击自动步枪”的缩写）无托突击步枪是一种专门为 CQB/城市作战设计的特种武器，由图拉仪器设计局 (KBP) 下属的中央运动及狩猎武器设计研究局 (TsKIB SOO) 应俄罗斯联邦安全局 (FSB) 要求而研制。该武器着重强化了极近距离的停止作用，针对 FSB 城市作战单位的常规作战环境进行了特化。",
      "en": "The ASh-12.7 (Avtomat Shturmovoy 12 - \"Assault Automatic Rifle 12\") bullpup assault rifle is a dedicated CQB/Urban Operations weapon, developed by TsKIB SOO (\"Central Design and Research Bureau of Sporting and Hunting Arms\"), a subsidiary of the KBP Instrument Design Bureau of Tula, Russia, by request from the Russian FSB (Federal Security Service). The weapon was designed with extreme short-range stopping power in mind for FSB urban combat units."
    },
    "weight": 6.865,
    "width": 4,
    "height": 2,
    "rarity": "Superrare",
    "backgroundColor": "black"
  },
